revision.text: ==English== ===Proper noun=== {{en-proper noun|Yarboughs}} # {{surname|en}}. ===Statistics=== * According to the 2010 United States Census, ''Yarbough'' is the 26949<sup>th</sup> most common surname in the United States, belonging to 900 individuals. ''Yarbough'' is most common among Black/African American (76.78%) and White (18.67%) individuals.
